===Etymology===
{{root|en|ine-pro|*pewH-}}
From {{suffix|en|compute|er|id2=agent noun}}.  {{doublet|en|cantore|counter|kontor}}

===Pronunciation===
* {{a|UK}} {{IPA|en|/kəmˈpjuːtə/}}
* {{audio|en|En-uk-computer.ogg|Audio (UK)}}
* {{a|US}} {{IPA|en|/kəmˈpjutɚ/|[kəmˈpʰjuɾɚ]}}
* {{audio|en|en-us-computer.ogg|Audio (US)}}
