=====Usage notes=====
* {{m|nl||Er}} is an unstressed variety of {{m|nl|hier}} and {{m|nl|daar}}, used when it is not needed to emphasize the specific location relative to the speaker.
* With a preposition, {{m|nl||er}} is used instead of {{m|nl|hem}}, {{m|nl|haar}}, {{m|nl|het}}, {{m|nl|ze}} to create a [[pronominal adverb]]. See also [[:Category:Dutch pronominal adverbs]].

