* From {{der|grc|ine-pro|*mō-}}, {{m|ine-pro|*mē-||endeavour, will, temper}}. Cognate with {{m|grc|μῶμαι||to seek after, meditate}}, {{m|grc|μαίομαι||to seek after}}, {{m|grc|μαιμάω||to be very eager}}, {{cog|la|mōs}}, {{cog|en|mood}}, {{cog|sla-pro|*sъmě̀ti}}.
