#* {{RQ:Pope Essay on Criticism|passage='''Stemm'd''' the wild torrent of a barbarous age.}}
# {{lb|en|skiing}} To move the feet apart and point the tips of the skis inward in order to slow down the speed or to facilitate a turn.

