==Portuguese==

===Etymology 1===
Merger of {{inh|pt|roa-opt|por}}, from {{inh|pt|VL.|*por}}, from {{inh|pt|la|prō||for}} (with metathetic shift due to {{m|la|per}}), and {{inh|pt|roa-opt|per}}, from {{inh|pt|la|per||through, by}}.

====Pronunciation====
* {{a|PT}} {{IPA|pt|/puɾ/|/poɾ/}}
* {{a|Brazil}} {{IPA|pt|/puʁ/|/poʁ/}}
** {{a|Paulista}} {{IPA|pt|[puɾ]|[puɹ]|[poɾ]|[poɹ]}}
** {{a|South Brazil}} {{IPA|pt|[poɾ]|[poɻ]|[puɾ]|[puɻ]}}
** {{homophones|pt|pôr}} {{qualifier|with /o/}}

====Preposition====
{{head|pt|preposition}}

# {{senseid|pt|on behalf of}} {{l|en|for}} {{gloss|on behalf of}}
#: {{ux|pt|Faça isso '''por''' mim.|Do this '''for''' me.}}
# {{senseid|pt|in order to obtain}} {{l|en|for}} {{gloss|in order to obtain}}
#: {{ux|pt|Espero '''por''' uma resposta.|I wait '''for''' an answer.}}
#: {{ux|pt|Eu farei de tudo '''por''' uma cópia deste livro.|I will do anything '''for''' a copy of this book.}}
# {{senseid|pt|over a period of time}} {{l|en|for}} {{gloss|over a period of time}}
#: {{ux|pt|Esperei '''por''' uma semana.|I waited '''for''' one week.}}
# {{senseid|pt|given in an exchange}} {{l|en|for}} {{gloss|''indicates something given in an exchange''}}
#: {{ux|pt|Ela deu sua bicicleta '''pela''' minha.|She gave her bicycle '''for''' mine.}}
# {{senseid|pt|through the action or presence of}} {{l|en|by}} {{gloss|through the action or presence of}}
#: {{ux|pt|A manutenção é feita '''por''' engenheiros.|The maintenance is carried out '''by''' engineers.}}
# {{senseid|pt|indicates the creator}} {{l|en|by}} {{gloss|''indicates the creator of a work''}}
#: {{ux|pt|Os livros '''por''' Tolkien são ótimos.|Books '''by''' Tolkien are great.}}
# {{senseid|pt|using the rules or logic of}} {{l|en|by}} {{gloss|using the rules or logic of}}
#: {{ux|pt|'''Pela''' lei, deveríamos estar presos.|'''By''' law, we should be in jail.}}
# {{lb|pt|mathematics}} [[times]], [[by]], multiplied by
#: {{ux|pt|oito '''por''' sete|eights '''times''' seven; eights '''by''' seven|inline=1}}
# {{senseid|pt|in the name of}} {{l|en|by}}; {{l|en|in the name of}} {{gloss|''indicates an oath''}}
#: {{ux|pt|Venceremos essa batalha, '''pelo''' rei!|We shall win this battle, '''by the''' king!}}
# {{senseid|pt|each}} {{l|en|per}}; {{l|en|a}}; {{l|en|each}} {{gloss|''expresses the ratio of units''}}
#: {{ux|pt|Tome uma pílula '''por''' dia.|Take one pill '''per''' day.}}
# {{senseid|pt|indicates a division}} {{lb|pt|arithmetic}} {{l|en|by}} {{gloss|''indicates a mathematical division''}}
#: {{ux|pt|Vinte '''por''' quatro é cinco.|Twenty '''by''' four is five.}}
# {{senseid|pt|through}} {{l|en|through}} {{gloss|entering and then leaving; being the medium of}}
#: {{ux|pt|Ainda passaríamos '''por''' muitos túneis antes de chegarmos.|We would still pass '''through''' many tunnels before we arrived.}}
#: {{ux|pt|Passar '''por''' uma situação difícil.|Go '''through''' a difficult situation.}}
# {{senseid|pt|near}} {{l|en|around}}; {{l|en|about}}; {{l|en|near}} {{gloss|in the vicinity of}}
#: {{ux|pt|O tesouro foi encontrado '''por''' Dudinka.|The treasure was found '''around''' Dudinka.}}
#: {{ux|pt|Gostamos de passear '''por''' aí.|We like to stroll '''around'''.}}
# {{senseid|pt|approximately}} {{l|en|around}}; {{l|en|about}}; {{l|en|approximately}} {{gloss|close in quantity, amount or value to}}
#: {{ux|pt|O preço de um prato nos mercados daqui é '''por''' vinte euros.|The price of a plate in the local markets is '''around''' twenty euros.}}
#: {{ux|pt|Partiremos '''pelas''' dez.|We will leave '''around''' ten.}}
# {{senseid|pt|throughout}} {{l|en|throughout}} {{gloss|in various parts of}}
#: {{ux|pt|Esse tipo de ruína é encontrado '''pela''' Escócia.|This type of ruin is found '''throughout''' Scotland.}}
# {{senseid|pt|in favour of}} {{l|en|for}}; {{l|en|in favour of}} {{gloss|supporting}}
#: {{ux|pt|Somos '''pela''' melhora da educação.|We are '''for''' the improvement of education.}}
# {{senseid|pt|for its own sake}} {{lb|pt|in the formula “X por Y”, where X is a clause and Y the infinitive of the verb in the clause, or of a synonym}} for its own sake; without a motive
#: {{ux|pt|Eu falei aquilo só '''por''' falar.|I said that just '''to''' say something.}}

=====Usage notes=====
''Por'' mandatorily contracts with definite articles in almost all circumstances:
* ''por'' + {{m|pt|o}} → {{m|pt|pelo}}
* ''por'' + {{m|pt|os}} → {{m|pt|pelos}}
* ''por'' + {{m|pt|a}} → {{m|pt|pela}}
* ''por'' + {{m|pt|as}} → {{m|pt|pelas}}

Contractions with indefinite articles and personal pronouns are uncommon and very colloquial:
* ''por'' + {{m|pt|um}} → {{m|pt|prum}}
* ''por'' + {{m|pt|uns}} → {{m|pt|pruns}}
* ''por'' + {{m|pt|uma}} → {{m|pt|pruma}}
* ''por'' + {{m|pt|umas}} → {{m|pt|prumas}}

