#: {{uxi|es|¡Bien '''por''' ti!|Good '''for''' you!}}
# [[via]], [[through]], [[by]] {{gloss|indicating the means of something}}
#: {{ux|es|Por favor, devuelva este documento completado '''por''' correo electrónico.|Please, return this document completed '''via''' email.}}
# [[for]] {{gloss|indicating duration}}
#: {{ux|es|Mi profesor se salió por la tangente '''por''' una hora entera.|My professor went off on a tangent '''for''' a whole hour.}}
# [[for]], [[for the sake of]], [[on behalf of]] {{gloss|indicating doing something for someone's benefit}}
#: {{uxi|es|No lo hago '''por''' ti.|I'm not doing it '''for''' your '''sake'''.}}
#: {{ux|es|Ella irá a trabajar '''por''' mí mañana.|She will be filling in '''for''' me at work tomorrow.}}
# [[per]], for each
#: {{uxi|es|Cuesta diez dólares '''por''' artículo.|It costs ten dollars '''per''' item.}}
# [[to]] {{gloss|indicating something that has not yet passed}}
#: {{uxi|es|Eso está '''por''' ver.|That remains '''to''' be seen.}}
#: {{uxi|es|La hora aún está '''por''' confirmar.|The time is yet '''to''' be confirmed.}}
# [[about to]] {{gloss|indicating something that will soon happen}}
#: {{ux|es|Su hermana está '''por''' llegar del aeropuerto en cualquier momento.|Her sister is '''about to''' arrive from the airport any minute now.}}
# [[compared to]]; [[against]]; [[versus]] {{gloss|indicating a comparison}}
