# {{senseid|en|inchoative}} {{n-g|When attached to certain [[adjective]]s, it forms a transitive verb whose meaning is,}} to [[make]] {{n-g|(adjective). Usually, the verb is [[ergative verb|ergative]], sometimes not. The same construction could also be done to certain (fewer) nouns, as, [[strengthen]], in which case the verb means roughly, "to give (noun) to", or "to become like (noun)".}}
