===Etymology 4===
From the {{der|de|grc|-ηνός}} feminine patronymic suffix.

====Pronunciation====
* {{IPA|de|/ˈeːn/}}

====Suffix====
{{head|de|suffix|cat2=noun-forming suffixes}}

# {{lb|de|chemistry}} [[-ene]] (alkene suffix)

