===Etymology===
From Old Galician and {{inh|gl|roa-opt|en}}, from {{inh|gl|la|in}}, from {{der|gl|itc-pro|*en}}, from {{der|gl|ine-pro|*h₁én||in}}.

===Pronunciation===
