# {{lb|fi|personal}} {{n-g|the first-person singular suffix for verbs}}
#: {{ux|fi|''lukea'' -> lue'''n''' "I read/am reading"|''kadottaa'' -> kadoti'''n''' "I lost (an item)"}}
#:* ''[[tulla]]'' -> [[en#Finnish|e]]'''n''' tule "I won't come/I'm not coming" (to express negation, the suffix is in the negation verb instead of the main verb)

