* Verbs from roots in {{m|ine-pro||*-h₃-}}. (e.g. {{m|la|dō}}, {{m|la|lavō}}, {{m|la|arō}})
* By sound laws acting on {{m|ine-pro|*-h₂}} + {{m|ine-pro|*-éh₁yeti}}. (singular case of {{m|la|stō}})

