##* {{quote-journal|en|date=2012-01|author=Donald Worster| volume=100| issue=1| page=70| magazine={{w|American Scientist}}| title=[http://www.americanscientist.org/bookshelf/pub/a-drier-and-hotter-future A Drier and Hotter Future]| passage=We may see many such [dust] storms in the decades ahead, along with '''species''' extinctions, radical disturbance of ecosystems, and intensified social conflict over land and water.}}
