Reanalysis of {{m-self|ga|do|t={{n-g|past tense marker}}}} and the early modern unstressed preverb {{m-lite|ga|do-}} of verbs like {{m-lite|ga|do-gheibhim|t=I get}}, {{m-lite|ga|do-chím|t=I see}} (and possibly also {{m-lite|ga|a-}} in {{m-lite|ga|a-tú|t=I am}}, {{m-lite|ga|a-deirim|t=I say}}) in relative clauses as a relative marker.

