#: {{syn|en|batch|flock|good deal|great deal|hatful|heap|load|lot|mass|mess|mickle|mint|muckle|peck|pile|plenty|pot|quite a little|raft|sight|slew|spate|stack|tidy sum|wad|whole lot|whole slew|Thesaurus:lot}}
