===Etymology===
From {{inh|en|enm|glas}}, from {{inh|en|ang|glæs}}, from {{inh|en|gem-pro|*glasą}}, possibly related to {{cog|gem-pro|*glōaną||to shine}} (compare {{m|en|glow}}), and ultimately from the {{der|en|ine-pro|-}} root {{m|ine-pro|*ǵʰel-||to shine, shimmer, glow}}. Cognate with {{cog|fy|glês}}, {{cog|nl|glas}}, {{cog|nds|Glas}}, {{cog|de|Glas}}, {{cog|sv|glas}}, {{cog|is|gler}}.

