#* '''1987,''' John Godber, ''Bouncers'' [http://books.google.com/books?ie=UTF-8&hl=en&id=f6-WVMj0qCUC&pg=PA19&lpg=PA19&sig=NzO0yHs5eqCDoOPewNE31SvzBBw page 19]:
